ygData.messageBody:
Hey I do too!

I have combined some bronze, blackened, and banded to create a pretty neat
combo. I like to use a tentacle whip when posing for pics ( as I lash the
photographer for full effect}. I refuse to wear a helmet, as DE female hair
looks better flowing free and my SK has the red eyes of hate as well.

Back to business. On the EQvaul developers board I have placed a post
regarding the SK pet, as other gripes are old. Please go to the Vault and
give your two copper. I feel the winds of change! They will not hear about
the HT issue anymore as they are well aware of our displeasure.

Enjoy our Nations B-day. Have a safe 4th and I'll talk to you all soon.

~Xillith
